name: Rhonda Pascual
text:
It was the best event salon I have ever been too and if they would do just a few things,I'd give them 5 stars. The staff should set up tables and chairs for people who attend events to sit on. Also,they need to place several trash cans around the perimeter of the dance.floor.
But overall,it is very nice ,in a rural community and the restrooms are well supplied and clean.Security is on the job,if anyone tried to fight or act out!
I.definitely recommend it!
